Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:19.91,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought it was kinda boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:22.74,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,that every day was the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:28.00,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I pretended it was someone \Nelse's fault that nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:35.13,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.63,0:01:03.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:08.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Waking up to a cat's backside...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:11.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,My adolescence is too \Nterrible for words.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:22.90,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Waking up to a human's backside \Nhas its own problems, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:26.33,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Goal: Escape from Sakura Hall!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:30.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai, please \Ndon't sleep here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.39,0:01:36.49,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be a bride when I grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:38.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,One of the rules of this world is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:40.18,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,spouting nonsense is only \Nacceptable if you're sleep-talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:42.33,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, honey. \NYou're back early.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:43.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a bride already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:45.35,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like dinner? Or a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.35,0:01:46.33,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:49.33,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,a loincloth?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:51.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a sumo ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:52.71,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,A brush?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:54.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Just get to the "Me?" part already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:56.31,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,However! Let's play a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:57.68,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Using that conjunction \Nmakes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:01:58.34,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pick up where we \Nleft off yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:01:59.71,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Not to mention, school starts today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:01.30,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, how about a \Nrule that requires me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:01.30,Saku-overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We have to get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:04.22,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to take off one article of \Nclothing every time you beat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:06.10,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You look ready to protect your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:07.15,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Get super excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:08.87,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just another \Npart of being young!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:10.56,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's climb the staircase to adulthood!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:13.11,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lust connection!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:15.47,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:19.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, what's with your \Nprovocative cleavage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:20.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The entrance ceremony's today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:24.34,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ceremonies are generally social \Ngatherings used for finding a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:26.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to put the \Nmoves on the new students?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:27.81,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:33.52,Sign,BOX,0000,0000,0000,,Toolbox
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:30.22,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,There might be some \Nhot single fathers there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:32.29,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:35.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:46.97,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:45.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to fix this broken sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:49.73,Saku-main,GIRL A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look, this is Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:53.38,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Suimei University of the Arts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:53.40,Saku-main,GIRL B,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the place where they stick\Nall of Suimei High's problem kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:54.88,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:57.23,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:03:04.72,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:03:00.29,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A collection of all the problem \Nkids at the high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:02.75,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,affiliated with Suimei University of the Arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:04.74,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Or in other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.13,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:12.42,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty hot without my clothes on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:16.05,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, a den of freaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.51,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:21.21,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The resident of Room 201:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:23.38,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Third year fine arts student, \NKamiigusa Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:29.08,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Kamiigusa Misaki\NFine Arts - Third Year\NHas Alien Qualities
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:25.90,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Designed, animated, wrote, and edited...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:27.67,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,her own anime all by herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:29.10,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,which was commercialized\N and became a smash hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:32.66,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun, you can't call \Nyourself a man if you run off...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:34.33,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,before we even get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:37.52,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Come! Let's leap into the world \Nof carnal desires together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:38.78,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Carnal desires?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:44.52,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:45.20,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:47.37,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The resident of Room 103:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:52.44,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Mitaka Jin\NGeneral Studies - Third Year\NHas Bourgeois Ladies' Man Qualities
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:50.15,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Scriptwriter on Misaki-senpai's anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:52.02,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and General Studies student, Mitaka Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:52.79,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.09,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:57.11,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,He comes home the following morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:03:58.80,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,in a manner unfit for a high school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:02.24,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Tomorrow I've got \Nthe race queen Suzune-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:04.48,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and this weekend, it's\N Rumi-san, the office lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:06.30,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll see the young \Nwife again next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:08.76,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Young wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:08.76,Saku-overlap,GIRLS,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else's wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:10.89,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Are you done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:15.26,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Art teacher, Sengoku Chihiro: \NThe supervisor of Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:18.92,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Sengoku Chihiro\NSupervisor\NHas Amazon Qualities
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:18.92,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}B: Ambition\NW: Dreams\NH: Hopes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:17.31,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's currently exceeded level 30...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:18.94,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and is looking for a husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:21.74,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 29 years and {\i1}15 months{\i0} old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:26.97,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Subject: Shut Up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:26.53,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,Subject: Shut Up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:35.81,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Sender: Akasaka Ryunosuke
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:30.78,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,Ryunosuke-sama has received \Nwork from S Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:33.46,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,He is currently in the \Nprocess of developing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.86,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,sound-compressing middleware.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:39.53,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,If you bother him, he will \Nsend you a virus, lol!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:40.50,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,From: Maid-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maid-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:46.06,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The resident of Room 102: \NAkasaka Ryunosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:49.74,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Akasaka Ryunosuke\NGeneral Studies - Second Year\NHas Hermit Qualities
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:48.21,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A second year General Studies \Nstudent and programmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:49.85,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,who already has contracts \Nwith major businesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:55.33,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The auto-reply AI mail program \Nhe created called Maid-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:58.00,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}"Those who ask rude questions such as 'How old are you \Nsupposed to be?' (Sorata-sama) will be firmly punished."\N-I am not "supposed to be" anything! (duh)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:57.30,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,is his only connection \Nto the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.02,Saku-overlap,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,He will send you a virus, lol!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:05:00.43,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we shouldn't bother him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:01.49,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to go again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:02.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:05.82,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Then, there's me, Kanda Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:10.81,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda Sorata\NGeneral Studies - Second Year\NOrdinary Qualities
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:09.05,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A General Studies student with average \Nlooks, average intelligence,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.78,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and no remarkable qualities whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:13.97,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,When you finish the sign, \Nstop by the faculty office...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:15.67,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,during lunch or whenever to let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:17.12,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and don't be late for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:21.72,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro-chan, good luck \Nwith your spouse hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:22.73,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't find anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:25.08,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,kouhai-kun said he'd marry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:26.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:31.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:34.56,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, \Nmy current goal is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:38.73,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,to escape this place! \NTo escape Sakura Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:41.96,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Goal: Escape from Sakura Hall!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:50.41,Saku-main,SPEECH,0000,0000,0000,,Suimei University of the Arts High School is \Ndivided into General Studies and the Arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:54.83,Saku-main,SPEECH,0000,0000,0000,,Our arts program is further divided \Ninto music and fine arts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:01.29,Saku-main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,You get all the bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:03.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miyahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:05.29,Saku-main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,A person of average willpower...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:07.88,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,could never handle living \Nin that den of freaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:10.09,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:13.34,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to stay \Nin Sakura Hall, Kanda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:14.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.32,Saku-main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nanami. You're in our class, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:18.56,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't leave soon, \Nit'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:20.55,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't found \Nanyone to take Hikari,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:22.31,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and you've taken in \Nsix more, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:24.33,Saku-main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,You must have no integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:26.13,Saku-main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,You keep bringing \Ngirls back to your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:28.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say things that'll \Ngive people the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:30.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,They'll think I belong in Sakura Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:32.25,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's ridiculous. That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:34.70,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:39.16,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking her home with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.33,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.63,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't keep her \Nin a regular dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.08,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do everything I can to \Nfind an owner for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:46.80,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just hide her until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:49.32,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What if someone finds her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.51,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cross that bridge when I come to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:55.76,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But, in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:07:02.40,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Principal
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:58.15,Saku-thought,PRINCIPAL,0000,0000,0000,,You must choose between...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:00.88,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,abandoning the cat or \Nleaving the regular dorms...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:02.40,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and taking up residence in Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.32,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What? Sakura Hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.36,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.51,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go to Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:07.32,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:12.51,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:13.56,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep getting more cats,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:17.03,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll never be able to come \Nback to the regular dorms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:19.31,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:21.91,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But ever since I took in Hikari,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:25.15,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been finding cats in \Ncardboard boxes everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:26.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Meow, meow, meow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:28.51,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but take care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:30.72,Saku-main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,You're definitely cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:34.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Cursed or not, \NI can't just leave them there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.35,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:37.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.00,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:42.00,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I-In any case, if you \Nreally want to get out of there,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:44.25,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you need to think more constructively.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:46.11,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Here, it's for Hikari and the gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:54.68,Sign,BAG,0000,0000,0000,,Conveni-Mart
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:48.15,Saku-main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Chikuwa, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.66,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I picked up some of the things...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:52.01,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we couldn't sell at the \Nconvenience store I work at.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.46,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's not normally allowed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:54.70,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but they made an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.72,Saku-main,DAICHI,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a lot on your plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.64,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're holding down a few jobs \Nat the moment, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:07:59.84,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:03.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do voice acting schools \Nreally cost that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:06.71,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You came here from Osaka on your own,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:16.28,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and you work so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:19.68,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,There are chances for me out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:20.37,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,General Studies  |  Arts
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:21.54,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,There are training schools,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:25.24,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and Kamiigusa-senpai let me \Ndo some voices for her anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:27.71,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,These aren't experiences \Nyou'd normally get.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:31.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, why don't you move...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:32.73,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,into Sakura Hall and take my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:35.57,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's a different matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:40.07,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talented like Kamiigusa-senpai \Nand everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:42.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I need to work hard in my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.60,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kanda. Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:50.74,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Did you fix the sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:52.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it won't budge an inch now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:53.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:08:55.52,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have any success \Nat the entrance ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:57.95,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,There weren't any hot single men.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:09:00.36,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I did exchange numbers with a \Nfew hot married men, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:02.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself a teacher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,At least be aware of your profession!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:04.96,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's shocking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:09.70,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot that before I even \Nleft my father's testes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:13.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time I've ever heard \Na woman say the word "testes!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:14.53,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Testes aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:16.11,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:19.84,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,She's my cousin, \Nand she'll be staying in...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.17,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:23.81,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mashiro
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:23.83,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,She's coming over from England. \NHer name is Shiina Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:26.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? She's staying at Sakura Hall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:27.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be good for her upbringing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:29.27,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Meet her at the station at six o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:30.79,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,And pick her up after school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:33.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I have to run another errand for you? \NWhat is this, a quest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.62,0:09:35.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you some kind of RPG barkeeper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:36.47,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:56.10,Saku-main,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:58.97,Saku-main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're Kanda's kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:00.82,Saku-main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,The mackerel's good today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:01.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:03.62,Saku-overlap,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata-kun! Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:06.29,Saku-main,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,I just fried some croquettes, \Nso take some with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:10.70,Saku-main,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata-kun, it can't be easy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:11.81,Saku-main,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuoka, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:14.38,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have gone with your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.57,Saku-main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:18.89,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,A time comes when a \Nman's gotta become a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:20.53,Saku-main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ambition! It's all about ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:23.28,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Flower Clark
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:21.66,Saku-main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Sorata?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.62,Saku-main,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,"Boys Meet Ambitions."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:28.29,Saku-main,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Meat. Eat your meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:31.78,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Ambition, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:43.14,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't thinking anything so daring...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:53.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I really should have \Ngone with my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:38.92,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:41.68,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What color do you want to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:45.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:48.43,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never really thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:49.97,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Then, think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't decided what I \Nwant to do in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:56.64,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but for now, I guess I'm iridescent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:57.48,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Iridescent?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:01.40,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What color do you want to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:04.07,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I've never really thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of answer is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:09.29,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment in time,\N I'm probably white.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:12.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Just like your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:16.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kanda Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:20.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro-sensei asked me \Nto come and meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:22.13,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:25.59,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How old is this photo she gave me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.78,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's at least three times older...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:32.81,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:36.00,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,somehow, I knew it was her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:39.27,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:42.07,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:43.70,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It has a beautiful ring to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:48.41,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:02.74,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:08.05,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Sakura Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:10.56,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We're having negima hotpot tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:13.68,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go! Ready and boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:16.31,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:18.20,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up, Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:19.11,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Here at Sakura Hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:21.74,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we always celebrate \Nby throwing a hotpot party!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:22.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:24.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,"Please place Ryunosuke-sama's \Nportion in a separate bowl,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:26.56,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and cover it with plastic wrap."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:28.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,"No onions. From: Maid-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.66,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Negima without onions? \NWouldn't that be just "ma"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:32.12,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Mashiron.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:34.50,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Have a thick, slimy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.68,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't bite it \Ncarefully and gently,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:38.13,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,hot juice will squirt out everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.07,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Squirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:40.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:41.99,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's with that \Ninnocent reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:43.44,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Convention dictates that \Nyou can only get excited...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.64,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,by vegetables until your \Nsecond year of middle school!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:46.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:49.39,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're from England, Mashiro-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:51.15,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to attend Suimei High, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:51.15,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:52.74,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,A transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:54.02,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,She's a second year art student.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Art?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:56.31,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:59.19,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Her height is 162 centimeters \Nand her weight is 45 kilos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:04.03,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,From the top down, that'd make her \N sizes around 79, 55, 78.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:04.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:05.90,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You think her breasts \Nare a little small?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:08.43,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act so disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:09.84,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,With such a small waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:12.41,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,her breasts will look bigger with no \Nclothes on than the numbers suggest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:13.73,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:15.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:17.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:20.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, she's usually really friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:21.70,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.65,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I will now screen the Mashiron...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:29.07,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,welcoming anime I made!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:29.07,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,When did you make that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:31.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you knew Shiina was coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:31.72,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Switch on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:39.14,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiron!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:43.74,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:49.53,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to Sakura Hall, boom, whoosh, bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:56.66,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be friends forever, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:15:01.58,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, rat-tat-tat, boom, boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:05.16,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:07.18,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,The voice-over and the content...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:09.16,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,have surprisingly little \Nto do with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:11.96,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,How is this a welcoming \Nanime for Mashiro-chan exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:14.36,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You just wanted to do a quick \Nscreen check for your new animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:15.60,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's also correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.27,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anything bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:19.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:22.76,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, it was kinda amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:24.28,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:26.43,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,The timing of the last explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:28.74,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you shift it back four frames?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:31.27,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're so right. \NIt does come in a little early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:32.82,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I could add some in-betweens or...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:35.47,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you add some white frames, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.61,0:15:36.72,Saku-overlap,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's hopeless once they start with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:37.46,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ah, I see. In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:40.76,Saku-overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I should probably make the \Nlighting effects stronger here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:41.96,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,They're usually a ridiculous pair,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:42.87,Saku-overlap,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Is the high contrast just \Nfor film processing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:44.88,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but they get serious when it \Ncomes to making animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:46.02,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yeah. I thought it'd work with \Nsome color correction, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:57.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good. She must \Nthink I'm worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:00.23,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If she's studying art,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:03.14,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,she must be unbelievably talented, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:08.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.61,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awfully moody today...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:16.05,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Goal: Escape from Sakura Hall!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.44,0:16:21.32,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought it was kinda boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:23.75,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,that every day was the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.74,0:16:29.21,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But, after taking in a pure \Nwhite cat over the summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:34.29,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,and coming to Sakura Hall, \NI finally realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:40.04,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't the days that were boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:46.46,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,but myself, for being like someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:53.70,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:56.53,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin, try and catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:57.66,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.47,0:17:01.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're all up early this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:03.08,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,So we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:05.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:07.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Shiina come to Sakura Hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:09.17,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't she have stayed \Nin the regular dorms?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:12.57,Sign,CUP,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.59,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Because this place suits her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:17.05,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You'll look after Mashiro, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:19.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is her first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:21.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll at least show her the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:25.16,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. Make sure you take \Nher there properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:28.06,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you take her \Nthere responsibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:33.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That was kinda creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:40.22,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Second Floor Girls' Dorm\NNo Boys Allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:40.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a choice. \NOrders are orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get ready \Nsoon, you'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:51.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:58.68,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Please Knock\NMashiron's Room
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:53.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:58.68,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She seriously isn't answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:01.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm opening the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:04.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:12.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A burglar? No, tornado damage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.91,0:18:14.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:16.73,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:17.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Where are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:20.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:24.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's incredibly good...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:31.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:33.83,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,They ran into each other on the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:35.24,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to school and fell in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:39.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the romantic rival \Nwho kept dropping hints go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:42.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:53.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:01.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Shiina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:04.57,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please wake up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:08.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's morning. It's morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:10.74,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Morning will never come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:14.08,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's here! \NDon't say such scary things!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:24.66,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:33.38,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:35.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:36.23,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:37.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Put some clothes on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you naked, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:39.99,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you one of {\i1}those{\i0} people?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:42.41,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why I'm naked...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:44.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Try to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.41,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I got in the bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:47.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You got in the bath! Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:48.38,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I took out my clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:49.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You got out of the bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:51.12,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now you just have to put them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:52.04,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I took everything out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:53.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:55.72,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the reason \Nthis room is so chaotic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:57.46,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I figured it \Ndidn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:59.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of thought process is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:01.22,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you took your clothes out, \Nthen wear them! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:09.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you decent?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:10.77,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:13.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I know you're from England,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:16.44,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm sure there are some \Ncultural differences, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's decent about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Put your clothes on already! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:20.31,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What about my underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:21.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Put them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:22.00,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But which ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:23.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me choose for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:24.70,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I won't wear any.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:25.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You have to wear some!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:27.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wear some! Put them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:28.23,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please put them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:30.49,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Here, pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:33.47,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,These panties aren't cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.47,0:20:34.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,They're yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.82,0:20:37.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap! Hey, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:38.71,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:43.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Your head! I mean, your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:45.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Go fix it in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:46.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,While you're at it, wash your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:51.54,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:55.25,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,My image of Shiina is \Nslowly crumbling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:56.28,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:57.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:00.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:02.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Put something on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:04.15,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Some kind of underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:06.13,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't put anything out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:08.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault? Don't you \Nthink that's kinda weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:13.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The floor's wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:16.33,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a custom of \Nbathing in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:18.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that lazy teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:21.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She pushed all of this onto me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:23.20,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Iridescent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:24.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:27.23,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:28.85,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a color?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:31.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. It's sort of rainbow-colored,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:34.85,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it means an ambiguous color, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:37.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking about that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.58,0:21:42.28,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, you're interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:50.74,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I took in a pure white \Ncat over the summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:52.47,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and moved into Sakura Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.72,0:21:57.21,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:21:59.81,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,that spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:09.15,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.40,0:22:12.17,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be late for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.17,0:22:14.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.76,0:22:19.69,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I met a pure white girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.83,0:22:22.70,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, you're so domineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.70,0:22:26.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Use your own legs to run, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:34.29,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1400,979)}#01: Cat - White - Mashiro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:33.83,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Today's panty forecast is:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:40.98,NextEptitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(489,1)}#02 I Drew a Picture
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.79,0:23:36.56,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Green panties represent...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.19,0:23:40.98,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,a possible storm brewing.
